{"tid":1954083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【幫手dislike爆佢！！】香港之恥SCMP CEO上TED讚中國控疫做得好","createTime":"2020-04-01T14:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T14:55:31.000Z","uid":319231,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ef07194774242d1369b3d79d138ca27348226972","tid":1954083,"uid":319231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:21:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫手dislike爆佢！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\nWhat the world can learn from China&rsquo;s response to the coronavirus | Gary Liu<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KIh2-S2jXls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKIh2-S2jXls&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUpS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=8cba9a1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KIh2-S2jXls</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">SCMP既CEO Gary Liu</span>上左TED talk，<br />\n用一個<span style=\"font-size: large;\">知識型既口吻分析</span>，<br />\n將中國既大話連篇，<br />\n編織返一個合理既故仔，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">叫各國學習中國點咩控疫！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTED Talks係youtube有1600萬subscribers，<br />\n聽眾全球都有，好有公信力，<br />\n聽眾多數都係高教育水平，<br />\n完全係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">國際輿論戰</span></span></span></ins></span>"},{"pid":"b1931b60f5b34b08cb13badd5d31b45451f4b433","tid":1954083,"uid":319231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:22:43.000Z","msg":"因為條友係咁讚，講漏左請原諒：<br />\n<br />\n- 中國個數字唔準確係因為定義唔同（冇病徵唔計數），而唔係中國特登隱瞞咼！<br />\n<br />\n- 雖然一開始中國有否定，有遏制消息，但之後已經好好！不斷share資訊，態度大變！<br />\n<br />\n- 李文亮發現，但第二日官方已經即刻承認有27單確診<br />\n<br />\n- 1月20號鍾南山承認人傳人，過左三日武漢就即刻封城，好快好果斷！<br />\n<br />\n- 習近平去得武漢參觀，就即係話已經控制得好好！<br />\n<br />\n- 再三重複，官方一路都唔知有武漢肺炎，十一月既個案係諗返轉頭覺得係武漢肺炎<br />\n<br />\n- 李文亮單野已經處理左，有警察受罰，警察向左家人道歉，無事咼！<br />\n<br />\n- 中國已經搞掂晒！就返復工啦！<br />\n<br />\n- 中國好叻呀！幫左好多人做病毒測試，隔離，追蹤接觸人士，所以控制得好好！"},{"pid":"8b36b51ad9ae2c4f25b0884d3cb7a95af6a4464f","tid":1954083,"uid":319231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:23:06.000Z","msg":"聽到都想嘔"},{"pid":"5bf40deb157a1aa5bb5165fb330c7454b288cef6","tid":1954083,"uid":319231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:24:16.000Z","msg":"但youtube入面既comments好buy"},{"pid":"55d99209d1da5d6d0f309ce3f48472b046712d24","tid":1954083,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14faae89719beafa0415fef583077eb26c604a57","tid":1954083,"uid":319231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:25:55.000Z","msg":"SCMP係佢領導下會點 即刻明晒"},{"pid":"2b212ae9e1faab5cd08919536b6e4e7a403f4ef4","tid":1954083,"uid":319231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:26:52.000Z","msg":"仲要話自己come from Hong Kong"},{"pid":"3a77551d7479c5cc6707856a7b1ee3d9c6e8b730","tid":1954083,"uid":319231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:27:09.000Z","msg":"影衰香港人"},{"pid":"b5fcc7b1ef56730924d3a3fc2ab0488e9e48655c","tid":1954083,"uid":319231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:27:28.000Z","msg":"Shame on you!!!"},{"pid":"ff4a2371658ed147824ba6fa5d50ed82f858ba48","tid":1954083,"uid":319231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:27:51.000Z","msg":"自推9/10"},{"pid":"5af520f4ba080aecf34f47bfbc8fba7f3290120a","tid":1954083,"uid":319231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:28:08.000Z","msg":"自推10/10"},{"pid":"ee903b293654749ba9545f2ab293